            <span class="text-gray-600">Document exact color codes (HEX, RGB, CMYK, Pantone) and use them consistently everywhere. Variations dilute brand recognition.</span>
          </li>
          <li>
            <strong>Mistake #6: Following Trends Over Timelessness</strong><br/>
            <span class="text-gray-600">Trendy colors feel dated quickly. Choose colors that will work for 5-10 years, not 6 months.</span>
          </li>
        </ul>
